    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good, solid condition and has been well-cared for, making it a wonderful choice for anyone seeking a reliable and attractive ride. While it shows some minor signs of its journey, it remains a dependable performer that is ready for many more miles. It's a great opportunity to own a quality car that balances value and performance perfectly!",
