    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably preserved vehicle, currently offered in pristine, showroom condition. Every aspect of this automobile\u2014from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously maintained interior\u2014reflects a standard of care that is rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure absolute mechanical integrity, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. This is an exceptional opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
